{"id":"b4698c45-58d6-4865-a6b8-a23b2b0e44fb","name":"Sōsō no Frieren RPG +18 v0.1","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 245, 220)\"><strong><em>\"You're taking Stark's place.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 245, 220)\">___________________</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 245, 220)\"><strong>Hey guys, I couldn't resist making an RPG of my previous bot, Frieren. And yes, even though I haven't added a status system yet, there are cities and a clear objective for now. I hope you enjoy this first version of this bot.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 245, 220)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Remember you can donate to my </mark></strong></span><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/sekithemc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 245, 220)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit\"><u>Ko-fi</u></mark></em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 245, 220)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit\"> account. Of course, this isn't mandatory; I do this as a hobby anyway, so I'll keep making bots as much as possible.</mark></strong></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"cqs32yIWYTQofiB4bUtt-.webp","creator":"SekiTheMC","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","🦄 Non-human","🧝‍♀️ Elf","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG"],"chats":2673,"messages":28356,"created_at":"2025-05-04T05:59:39.896194+00:00"}